<div id="Idea_3586"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3586-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3586">President Obama is Obstructing Justice&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/6573-4049">brent</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">4 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">We should all let Pres Obama know that his "look forward" position ON TORTURE (AND OTHER CRIMES) is tantamount to obstruction of justice.<br/><br/>He should remove his "bias" from the equation; and let AG Eric Holder do his appointed job which is to PROSECUTE KNOWN CRIMINAL ACTIONS--OF WHICH THERE ARE SEVERAL. The first step would be to appoint a SPECIAL PROSECUTOR.<br/><br/>Mr Obama, please stop being an OBSTRUCTIONIST.</div>
